// V12.0 CHANGELOG:
// - CRITICAL FIX (Headings): Rewrote 'detectHeadingLevel'.
//   - It now correctly handles text with or without a space (e.g., "##Heading" vs "## Heading").
//   - It now *guarantees* the removal of all hash prefixes from the returned text.
//
